OL,5,Cfor Boohoo
OL,6, Boohoo has reported a 41% rise in
OL,7, full-year sales as home working fuelled
OL,8, demand for athleisure, making up for a
OL,9, slump in "going out" gear.
OL,11,FThe online retailer said customers
OL,12,Fbought more activewear and loungewear
OL,13,Fduring the pandemic.
OL,15,FBut it saw "significant declines" in
OL,16,Fareas such as dresses and "going out"
OL,17,Fclothes due to Covid lockdowns.
OL,19,FOver the year, Boohoo bought a number
OL,20,Fof High Street brands which foundered
OL,21,Fin the pandemic, including Debenhams.
